      "kind": "diagnostic",
      "code": "COMPRESSOR_OUTLET_PRESSURE_TARGET_TOO_CLOSE",
      "message": "Recycle Compressor outlet pressure target is too close to the inlet pressure to explain the requested compression duty."
    },
    {
